Deputy President William Ruto held a meeting with a section of leaders from Wajir county at his official Karen residence on Wednesday. &nbsp;The leaders, drawn largely from the Degodia community, were led by Eldas MP Adan Keynan (ODM). According to Keynan, the meeting was to discuss the drought situation in the county. Mohamed Elmi (Tarbaj ODM), Abbas Sheikh Mohamed (Wajir East URP), ODM nominated senator Halima Abdille, Ahmed Kolosh (aspirant Wajir West), Ibrahim Rashid (ODM elections board member), and former NSSF chairman Aden Mohamed attended the meeting.